## State Machine Summary

| State | resolvedReview | Active warning | Trigger |
|-------|---------------|----------------|---------|
| Normal play | null | hidden | — |
| Review position active | null | visible | ghost targets blunder |
| User moved at review | `{ moveIndex, 'pending' }` | hidden | `applyPlayerMove` (sync) |
| Analysis returned | `{ moveIndex, 'pass'\|'fail' }` | hidden | `AnalysisEffects` (guarded) |
| New review + resolved | `{ moveIndex, 'pass'\|'fail' }` | visible | ghost targets new blunder |
| User moves again | null | hidden (or new pending) | `applyPlayerMove` clears first |
| Late analysis after clear | null (ignored) | — | moveIndex mismatch → skip |
| Game ends (any path) | null | hidden | handleGameEnd/resign/reset/etc. |
| Browsing history | unchanged but hidden | hidden | `isViewingLive` gate |

