## Manual Verification

1. Start ghost game, reach review position (warning toast appears)
2. Make a move — toast transitions to dimmed pending with no flicker
3. Wait for analysis — green checkmark or red X overlays the toast
4. Navigate back in history — overlay hides; return to live — reappears
5. Make another move — resolved box clears
6. Trigger revert during pending state — box clears
7. Start new game — box clears
